# Runtime-generated trained model artefacts directory. Scoped to the backend/
# working directory so it doesn't accidentally match the `app/models/` Python
# package (which introduced a silent ignore of app/models/_db_backend.py in
# commit 11356184, producing a ModuleNotFoundError on Jenkins builds).
/models/
